'''Sod vavr''' borovpi sodanch sodta, punzayta, topasta, parkita, foddnni (''analysis'') korta, mellovnni (''synthesis'') korta ani je nixkorx (''conclusions'') melltat, borovpi aplie pod’dotin te loka mukhar dovorta.  Boro borovpi sodanch xikpi, chintpi, sod lavpi ani novem ghoddovpi, vegllem kitem tori divpi, aplem khaxeleponn samballpi asta.  To novem polleta, vo adlem asa tem nove nodren polleta, tacher niyall korta.

'''0. Sod vavrachem mhotv:'''
'''Sod''' vavr korun kelolie khoinche-i borpavollik lambay, runday, kholay ani unchay asta.  Haka lagun borovp, vachpiank chodd faideachem zaum yeta ani aple vichar manddta.  Haka lagun vachpiancher vhoikari (''positive'') probhav poddum yeta. Tanchi vachpachi ruch bodlum yeta. Tankam novi dixa ani nodor mellta.  Sod vavrak lagun borpavollicho panvddo sudarta ani dorjedar sahitya toyar korunk hatbhar lagta . 

'''1.0	 Sod vavr keloli Romi Konknni borpavoll:'''
Romi Konknnint sod vavr korun keloli borpavoll kaim promannant asa. Jezvit Padri Antonio Pereirachim pustokam ghetlim zalear tantlim chodd-xim pustokam tannem sod vavr korun boroyleant. Dekik Saibinnicher boroylolem pustok ''Dhortorevoili Sundori; Fuddari:Sant Inas de Loyola; Kalljidar:Sant Fransisk Xaveir; Jezuchim Komllam:Jezvit Sant Bhokt; Kunkollechea Jezvit martirancher boroylolem Saxttichi Tambddi Mati; Zuze Vazacher boroylolem  Zatrekar Jose; Gõyche Dhortorevoilo Pri Agnel; Gõychem Mannik:Padr Agnel; Konknni Xastri Dalgado; Konknni Oparinchem Bhanddar; Anvddeancho Monis: Sant Vincent Pallotti'' ani her tachim kaim pustokam.

Jezvit Padri Moreno de Souzan boro sod vavr korun ''Tisvaddecheo Igorzo<ref>Published by Thomas Stephens Konknni Kendr, Alto Porvorim, Goa</ref>''; ''Bardescheo Igorzo ani Saxtticheo Igorzo bhag 1 ani 2'' buk boroyleat.  Fr. Ave Maria Afonsochem ''Rendermam’ ani Tachem Jivit''; A. Carvalhochem ''Madd ani Tacho Upiog''; Nevil Alphonsochem ''Nal’lachi Lagvodd'', Fr. Planton Fariachem ''Kunkolle Ek Mahan Ganv'', Jezvit padri Matthew Almeidachem ''Romi Lipient Konknni Kors<ref>Published by Thomas Stephens Konknni Kendr, Alto Porvorim, Goa</ref>'', Bonaventure D’ Pietrochem ''Songit Doulot Goenkaranchi'', Jose Pereirachem ''Konknni Bhagti Gitam'' he buk sod vavr korun boroyleat.  

Sod vavr koso korcho ho prosn zaitiank poddta.  Sod vavr kortoleamni poilim apnnakuch kaim mullave ani mhotvache prosn vicharunk zay ani tanchio zapo sodunk zay. Te prosn he:
1.	Mhaka kitem zay?  Hoch prosn matso vegllie toren vicharum yeta. Mhaka khoinchea vixoyacher sod vavr korunk zay?  
2.	Mhaka to vixoy kiteak zay? vo to vixoy hanvem kiteak vinchla?
3.	Tea vixoyak lagu zaloli mahiti mhaka khoim melltoli? Konna lagim melltoli? Kitli melltoli? Kednam melltoli ani ti koxi melltoli?
4.	Punzaylolie mahiti thaun kitem ani kitlem hanvem gheunchem?
5.	Ti mahiti hanv kitem kortolom/lim?

Hea prosnanchea zapancher adarun sod vavrak hat ghalcho poddta.  He voile prosn ami fokot sod vavr kortanam mat nhoy bogor jivitant vinchnni korchea vellar vichartanv.  Orthabhorit jivit jiyeunk he prosn chodd gorjeche ani faideache.

Ek boro lekh, pustok, kotha, kadom’bori, nattok, tiatr boroytanam vinchlolea vixoyacher sod vavr korun boroylear ti borpavoll borich kholayechi ani probhavi zata.  Dekik Gõyche roste ani bazar nitoll korpi kamgaranchea jivitacher ek kadom’bori borounk konnem fuddakar ghetlo zalear tannem/tinnem tea kamgaranchi bhas thoddi tori xikchi poddtoli. Uprant tanchea ghoramni vochun tankam mellun tanche lagim uloun, tanchem jivit, jivita kodde tanchi nodor, tanche prosn, tanchio oddchonni, tanche achar, riti-rivaz somzun ghevun, tannim kam’ korchea zageamni vochun tanchi kam’ korchi rit, thoinchi poristhiti somzun gheun tanchea jivitacher adarun ani apli thoddi kalponikota (''imagination'') vaprun bori kadom’bori borounk zata. 

Sod vavr don prokarancho asta. Poilo bhitor bosun kelolo sod vavr.  Oslo sod vavr korpi apleach ghorant bosun vo vachpa ghoramni vochun pustokam, nemallim vachun, vebsaitti polleun sod korta.  Dusrea prokaracho sod vavr asa to moll obheas (''Field study'').  Hea prokaracho sod vavr korunk zaite kodde vechem poddta.  

'''2.0	 Sod vavr korchi rit:'''

'''2.1 Vixoy vinchop:''' 
Vixoy vinchtanam voir dilolea prosnanchio zapo motint dhorchio poddtolio.  Te bhair ani kaim gozalincher chit diunchem poddtolem.  Dekik, vincholea vixoyacher obheas korunk mhoje lagim kitlo vell asa?  Obheas korchi takot mhoje lagim asa?  Obheasa khatir pois vechem poddtolem?  Obheas korunk zay aschim sadhonam mhoje lagim asat vo mhojea vottharant tim melltat?  Obheas korunk kitlo khorch lagtolo?  Hanvem vinchlolea vixoyacho konnak ani kitlo upyog zatolo?  Sod vavr korunk mhaka konn vatt dakhoytolo/li?  Sod vavr kortoleamni hea prosnank zapo sodunk zay.

Sod vavr korunk vixoy kaim unne nant.  Te sodun bhonvchi goroz nam.  Te amchea vottharant vo ganvantuch melltat.  Tantle kaim vixoy he.  
