'''3. Sod vavrachi ankhnni:'''
Vinchun kaddlolea vixoyacher sod vavr kortanam tacho vistar kitlo astolo, sod vavr korchi rit, vellachi ani khorchachi yevzonn hancher vichar korcho poddta.  Dekik renderacher obheas korunk vixoy vinchlo zalear, akhea Gõychea render somazacher obheas zatolo vo tharavik vottarachea renderancho obheas zatolo hem tharaunk zay.  Render somazak som’bond zalolea sorv vixoyancher obheas zatolo vo kaim vinchlolea vixoyancher obheas zatolo hem adi fuddench chintunk zay.  Toxench tea obhyasant sur kaddchi rit, surechi fenni, godd ani xirko korchea ritincho aspav astolo vo na hacho-i vichar zaunk zay. Renderanchim kantaram, avtam (tools) ani tanchea vavrak sombon’d zalole achar, vidhi ani dharimik riti hancher sod vavr zatolo vo na tem tharaunk zay.  Jitli sod vavrachi ankhnni bori zata tea mapan sod vavr boro zata.

'''4. Mahiti ekttaim korop:'''
Mahiti mellche zage ani mahiti ekttaim korchi rit oxe don bhag hea vixoyant aspavtat.

'''4.1 Mahiti mellche zage:'''
Sod vavr kortanam kalponik vichar vo purave naslolim motam manddunk zainant.  Puraveancher adarun  aple vichar manddche poddtat.  Purave mellunk mahiti ekttaim korchi poddta.  Sod vavrak zay, ti mahiti amkam vachpa ghoramni (''libraries''), doftorkhaneamni (''archives''), sorkari khateamni, vostu songrohaloyamni (''museums''), khasgi songrohamni (''private collection''), prodorxonamni (''exhibitions'') mellta. Toxench molleamni, bagamni, kullagoramni, xetamni, dongramni, ganvamni ani soimbant mellta.  Toxench ti mahiti zannkaram lagim, zannteam lagim ani tea tea vixoyachea mon’xam lagim vochun ekktaim korunk zata.  Reddio, TV, CD, DVD, kesetti, fotte, chitram, filmam, vebsaitti oslea prosar madhyomamni (''mass media'') amkam mahiti mellta.

'''4.2 Mahiti ekttaim korchio riti:'''
Mahiti ekttaim korchio kaim riti asat. Sod vavrachea vixoya pormannem mahiti ekttaim korchi rit vinchchi poddta.  Tantli ek vo eka poros chodd riti vaprun mahiti ekttaim korunk zata. 

'''4.2.1 Prosnavoll(''questionnaire''):'''
Prosnavoll toyar korun zanche koddlean amkam mahiti zay tankam ti dhaddchi. Mahiti boroun zatoch, tim mon’xam prosnavoll amkam pattim dhaddtat.  Hi pod’dot vaporlear somest mon’xam amkam zapo boroun dhaddtolim hachi khatri nam.  Prosnavoll gheun ami mahiti ditolea mon’xam lagim vochun zapo boroun ghetlear kam’ vegim zata ani sarkem zata.  Amchea khatrechea mon’xank torbeti (''training'') diun tanche lagim prosnavolli diun zapo boroun haddunk laylear kam’ azun vegim zata.

'''4.2.2 Mulakhot:'''
Mahiti ami mulakhot gheun ekktaim korunk zata ani tantlean khup mahiti mellounk zata.  Mulakhot ami tonddi vo fonar gheunk zata. Mulakhoti vellar ami mulakhot ditoliank kaim prosn vichartanv ani tanchea zapancher adarun tankam fuddle prosn vicharunk zatat.  Fonar ghetlole mulakhoti poros mon’xank mellun tonddi mulakhot ghetloli chodd faideachi.

'''4.2.3 Nirikxonn (''observation''):'''
Zea vixoyacher amkam sod vavr korunk zay tea vixoyak som’bond zalolea zageamni vochun, nirikxonn korun ami mahiti ekttaim korunk zata.  Nirikxonn don prokaramni korunk zata. Vantto ghevpi nirikxonn ani vantto ghe naslolem nirikxonn.  Vantto ghevpi nirikxonnant, nirikxonn kortolo vixoyant vantto gheta. Dekik dhaleacher obheas kortolo/li dhaleanchea gitamni ani nachant vantto gheun svotachea onnbhovan sod vavr korta.  Vantto ghe naslolea nirikxonnant, sod vavr korpi dhaleachea manddar veta ani fokot dhalo polleun obheas korta. 

'''4.2.4 Stithi obheas (''case study''):'''
Eka mon’xacher, ekie sonvsthecher va eka somudayacher kholayen obheas kortanam stithi obheas pod’dot vaportat. Vixoyacho pattlo itihas, tachi vaddavoll, tache prosn, oddchonni, ani onnbhov hancher sod vavr korcho poddta. 

'''4.2.5 Nomuno obheas (''sample study''):'''
Jednam vixoyacho vistar khup vhodd asta, tednam soglleancher obheas korunk zainam. Oslea vellar kaim nomune gheun tancher obheas korun nixkorx kaddche poddtat.  Dekik Gõyant bhurgim aplem iskolachem xikop ordear kiteak soddtat ho vixoy gheum-ia. Iskol soddlolea bhurgeancho ankddo vhodd aslolean dor eka bhurgea lagim vochun obheas korunk zaunchem nam. Mhonntoch taluka pormannem kaim sorkari ani khasgi iskolanche nomune gheun obheas korcho poddtolo. Hea obheasachea adaracher jeral nixkorx kaddche poddtat.

'''5.0 Mahitichi vanttnni:'''
Ekttaim keloli mahiti khup asum yeta. Tantli amkam khoinchi gorjechi ti vinchun vixoya pormannem tiche lhan lhan vantte korun, foddnni ani mellovnni korun nixkorx kaddche poddtat.  Nixkorxancher adarun puraveam soit amche vichar toyar korunk zatat.

'''6.0 Sod vavracher adarun borpavoll:'''
Sod vavrachem kam’ zatoch mell’loli mahiti ani nixkorx vaprun lekh, pustok vo her borpavoll korum yeta.  Sod vavr kortanam vixoyak som’bond zalole her prosn vo vixoy upzaleat zalear te lekhant manddlole bore.  Haka lagun fuddem her konnak tea vixoyancher sod vavr korunk vatt ugti zatoli.

'''7.0 Sompovnni:'''
Konknnichi borpavoll dorjedar zaunk zay, tika kholay zay, her bhasanchea panvddeak ti pavunk zay tor sod vavr chodd gorjecho.  Lokak kitem zay tench amche borovpi dit ravle zalear te posorkar zaun urtole.  Apnnem lokak kitem diunk zay hacho vichar korche borovpi sod vavr korun apli borpavoll kortole ani itihasant takotdar ani vicharvont borovpi mhonn omor zatole.  Amchea tornattea borovpiamni sod vavr, aplie borpavollichi buniad korun ghetli zalear Romi Konknni sahitya unchlea panvddear pavtolem.
